#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.gt.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.gt"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.arithmetic._install.<locals>._register_bin_method.<locals>.call_df_fill:1
#: of
msgid ""
"Get Greater than of dataframe and other, element-wise (binary operator "
"`gt`). Among flexible wrappers (`eq`, `ne`, `le`, `lt`, `ge`, `gt`) to "
"comparison operators."
msgstr ""
"获取 DataFrame 和 other 的逐元素大于比较（二元运算符 `gt`）。在比较运算符"
"的灵活包装器（`eq`, `ne`, `le`, `lt`, `ge`, `gt`）中的一种。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.arithmetic._install.<locals>._register_bin_method.<locals>.call_df_fill:5
#: of
msgid ""
"Equivalent to `dataframe > other` with support to choose axis (rows or "
"columns) and level for comparison."
msgstr "等价于 `dataframe > other`，支持选择比较的轴（行或列）和层级。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.arithmetic._install.<locals>._register_bin_method.<locals>.call_df_fill
#: of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.arithmetic._install.<locals>._register_bin_method.<locals>.call_df_fill:8
#: of
msgid "Any single or multiple element data structure, or list-like object."
msgstr "任意单个或多个元素的数据结构，或类列表对象。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.arithmetic._install.<locals>._register_bin_method.<locals>.call_df_fill:10
#: of
msgid ""
"Whether to compare by the index (0 or 'index') or columns (1 or "
"'columns')."
msgstr "按索引（0 或 'index'）还是列（1 或 'columns'）进行比较。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.arithmetic._install.<locals>._register_bin_method.<locals>.call_df_fill:13
#: of
msgid ""
"Broadcast across a level, matching Index values on the passed MultiIndex "
"level."
msgstr "跨层级广播，在传入的 MultiIndex 层级上匹配索引值。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.arithmetic._install.<locals>._register_bin_method.<locals>.call_df_fill
